reviews.text:
A restaurant that you will be surprised with the food quality and the wonderful service.
The location is not very close to the MTR while it’s worthwhile to visit.
Have booked via an app. with discount, which make you even worth to try. Food is very good esp the risotto & the soup, so creamy!
Have ordered two coffee, both very nice; and the dessert was perfect to end the tea on a Sat which you have 3 hours to chit chat with friends without any bother from the waiters!
5 stars food & services, why not go and try?! 🤨

Very nice little bistro. Staff are very friendly and efficient. Good for a nice lunch. I ordered the cream of truffle soup and pan fried salmon with champagne sauce. The food is excellent and very tasty. It is inside the shopping centre and there are no views. This restaurant is packed full during lunch times. Pricing is moderate.

The iberico pork rack, crab meat angel hair pasta, 10 oz. sirloin and rack of lamb are also delicious. One of the better quality establishments in Kwun Tong.
The staff of this restaurant are mostly kind. The food quality is very good. The atmosphere in the restaurant is good. Overall the restaurant is good, because of the above factors.
Good food and beer but cocktail not very good. Service is fine except that we are not informed our beer is buy 2 get 1 free when we check out 😑
Food quality good
